title: Khokababu
subTitle: Abir Roy falls in love with his employer's younger sister. His employer, however, happens to be a dangerous gangster and is overprotective of his sister.

title: Honeymoon That Changed Her Life
subTitle: Nikhil and Payel travel to a hill station for their honeymoon. But their trip turns out to be a nightmare when the hotel manager tries to molest Payel.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Parvati punishes Nikumbha for his misbehaviour in the name of Lord Shiva. However, Nikumbha pleads for forgiveness before Parvati.

title: Mone Pore Aajoshei din
subTitle: Rahul, a producer of a reality show, suffers from a terminal illness but decides to live life to the fullest. On a vacation, he meets Sunaina, a dancer, and falls in love with her.

title: Nawab
subTitle: Nawab, a police officer, does everything he can to fight injustice. However, his path is not as easy as it seems and is filled with hurdles.

title: Manik
subTitle: Samir Mitra impersonates his deceased friend to get a job. Later, when he falls in love with his employer's daughter and mutual relations meet, his identity is questioned.

title: Wanted
subTitle: The police kill Shibu, an innocent man, after mistaking him to be his lookalike Raja, an assassin. To escape from the police, Raja starts living with Shibu's parents as their son.

title: Barood
subTitle: Shaon, a loafer, and Jui, an innocent girl are in love with each other. They want to live the life of their dreams together but circumstances turn their lives upside down.

title: Paribar
subTitle: Rahul ventures into the smuggling business and lands in trouble. However, his brother Sagar takes the blame to protect him and their family.

title: Paribar
subTitle: Rahul ventures into the smuggling business and lands in trouble. However, his brother Sagar takes the blame to protect him and their family.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Nikumbha sets out to avenge Parvati by transforming himself into a horde of ants to attack her. However, his plan is thwarted when Lord Shiva comes to protect Parvati.

title: Shooter
subTitle: Following the death of his friend, Bobby decides to leave the army, but he is soon asked to come back into action in order to help prevent the assassination of the President.

title: Ghar Sansar
subTitle: An honest police officer single-handedly raises his sister and two brothers and does everything for them. However, an ongoing smuggling case eventually threatens to harm his family's well-being.

title: Kencho Khunrte Keute
subTitle: Gyanoda loses his son and daughter-in-law, leaving his granddaughter Parama as a spoilt child. To discipline her, he leaves a will which requires her to marry to gain full inheritance access.

title: Challenge
subTitle: Pooja, the daughter of a ruthless businessman who cannot tolerate any male advances towards her, falls for Abir. However, when her father learns about their relationship, all hell breaks loose.

title: Shiva
subTitle: When a police inspector manages to capture a member of a human trafficking ring, the gang leader vows to take revenge. He relentlessly hunts for the officer with an intention to kill him.

title: Sathi
subTitle: A singer accidentally causes a woman to lose her sight. Driven by guilt, he decides to help her achieve her dreams, while she remains unaware of his identity.

title: Bojhena Shey Bojhena
subTitle: A tragic love story intertwines the lives of four strangers, leading to unexpected bonds and heartbreak, forever altering their paths after a devastating accident.

title: Bojhena Shey Bojhena
subTitle: A tragic love story intertwines the lives of four strangers, leading to unexpected bonds and heartbreak, forever altering their paths after a devastating accident.

title: Abirbhab
subTitle: Tapen returns to his village after a long time and learns that the landlord and his son are troubling the villagers. He then vows to teach them a lesson and end their tyranny.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Lord Shiva leads Parvati's household to meet her, determined to distract her attention. However, Parvati insists on continuing her fast in order to prove her devotion.

title: Bhalobasar Dibbi
subTitle: Mahendra and Laxmi love each other and wish to get married but their wedding is called off when he is accused of rape. He is then ordered to marry the victim, filling Laxmi's father with rage.

title: Rupban Kanya
subTitle: A troubled king seeks answers to a devastating drought and his long-awaited heir. When a sage offers a blessing, fate takes an unexpected turn, shaping the kingdom's future.

title: Annadata
subTitle: Sankar's life changes when he gets taken in by a rich businessman. Years later, an opportunity arises for him to prove his loyalty to his adopted family.

title: Mahaguru
subTitle: Rudra Sen, a brave officer and an encounter specialist, is killed in the line of duty by a gangster. However, things become complicated when his doppelganger decides to take his place and avenge him.

title: Villain
subTitle: Riya meets Sneha on a flight back home and they strike up a conversation. Surprisingly, Sneha's fiance turns out to be a lookalike of Riya's boyfriend, leaving her in a state of shock.

title: Sejo Bou
subTitle: A poor man falls in love with a girl belonging to a wealthy family. In an attempt to separate them, the man is sent abroad. However, the couple's destiny intervenes, striving to bring them together.

title: Chore Chore Mastuto Bhai
subTitle: John is hired by Nagraj to steal a diamond but ends up betraying him, inviting his ire. Before Nagraj's henchman kills John, he gives the diamond to a taxi driver for safekeeping.
